---
title: Ultimate Beef & Caramelised Bacon-Onion Burger with Wedges, Cheddar Cheese & Burger Sauce
description: A juicy burger is the answer to your craving. Take a big bite and enjoy the caramelised onion and bacon on top of a tender beef patty, slathered in a layer of burger sauce. Dip the golden wedges into any leftover sauce because what burger would be complete
without a side of wedges.
